Download Raspbian here: https://www.raspberrypi.org/downloads/raspbian/
Use Balena etcher to install Raspbian on sd card https://www.balena.io/etcher/
Install mosquitto : https://www.instructables.com/id/How-to-Use-MQTT-With-the-Raspberry-Pi-and-ESP8266/
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get dist-upgrade
Setup screen : https://github.com/goodtft/LCD-show



